     Doriana made her way back from the communal bathing area after a particularly long soak in a very hot bath.  She felt extremely relaxed and it showed in the slow way in which she walked back to her hut.  Not only was she relaxed but her mind was on more pleasant things and they all included a small blonde healer.  <br>
     It's said that when a warrior's mind is preoccupied that makes them the most vunrable and this time was no exception.  Before she even know what was happening a tarp was thrown over her head and then she felt ropeing around her upper torso, trapping her arms to her side, and another rope around her legs, keeping her from kicking out.  She struggled and even threw off a few people, but then others joined in effectivly trapping her and lifting her to carry her out of the village.  <br>
     Her first thoughts were to the village guards and how they allowed what seemed to be a small army in their home.  They would be drilling for days, if she had anything to say about it.  Her second thought was all the plesantness she would be missing out on this night.  <br>
     Her captors were carrying her for what seemed like a candlemark when they set her down roughly propped up next to a tree.  She could hear them breathing heavily and she mentally rolled her eyes.  It seemed fitting she would get kidnappers that were out of shape.  <br>
     After a short rest she was lifted again and they were on their way.  She listened to the sounds around her and from the way the mens feet landed on the earth she could tell it was more then likely rock, which meant they were headed up into the mountains.  Taking the more difficult way, where they.  Well not only were they out of shape, but they were morons too.  That only angered her more.  She was put out with herself for ever letting these hades be damned idiots get the drop on her.  <br>
     She tried to distinguish how many different men there were, she was sure of at least four, because she could make out at least that many distinctive voices whispering to each other.  She didn't know their language so therefore she wasn't able to pinpoint where they were from.  Thinking to herself, 'This is going to be fun, I have no idea what they are saying, so I have no idea what they want.'  No matter she was going to kick their sorry asses when they get to where they were going anyhow. <br>
