     <br>
     She was getting more and more tired and cold.  She certainly didn't leave the baths this morning wearing her warmest clothing.  What bother her more was the fact that she didn't know if these men had taken her to sell as a slave as so many of their Amazon sisters had been or if they knew her position in the tribe and we going to ransom her.  She was certainly not going to let that happen.  Hades with these men if they tried to put her tribe in some sort of danger.  <br>
     <br>
     The men continued to talk in their mother tongue quietly to each other.  After what seemed like another few candlemarks they stopped and she was tugged to a halt.  At this point it was pretty hard to feel her hands, they had gone numb some time ago.  She was jerked off to her side and stumbled over, landing her shoulder into a tree.  She was pushed down and tied securely to the tree.  She didn't know if they were at their destination or if this was a night stop.  <br>
 <br>
     Dori had stayed quiet throughout the whole ordeal, but she needed to move her hands or else she was concerned that it could do permanant damage.  She felt one of the  men kneel next to her to check her bindings.  &quot;Hey, can you at least untie me so I can move my hands.  And how about a little food.&quot;  It seemed it wasn't the smartest thing to do, since the man yelled at her in his language and then she felt the side of his boot connect with her temple.  There really wasn't much after that except darkness. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=queenchiara>Queen Chiara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#993300>(2/24/03 9:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm55.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/cslrwillow/images/chiarasig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Your Worst Nightmare&quot;</span><hr size=1> Chiara found her sister queen, Rhiannon, and told her of her concerns.  <br>
