is mission. Leila sighed but reluctantly left her beloved staff behind. She was wickedly good with it, pretty darn fast with both short and long staves, but her first - her training staff - would always remain her favorite. Perhaps because it was with that staff that she made her intentions known as a small child: She would remain in the village, and become an amazon. She didn't want to go back to the tiny farm she'd grown up on, with the small hope of finding family there. She'd stay - stay with the Queens, the warriors - Zoe ... her friends. <br>
